Subject: Hardened Paths
Description: Hello, I have run an AD Health scan multiple times and the Hardened Paths continues to pop up. The customer has a GPO currently implemented at the top of the domain configuring hardened paths. Why does PC say there are no GPOs created?
What_We_Know__c:
Customer confirmed there is one forest/domain and the GPO is linked to the root of the domain.
It seems that could be an issue with the connection to the \DOMAINSYSVOL share
Next_Steps__c:
Customer need to check the values for their hardened UNC paths as there are some quotes not expected. 
Customer will be adjusting this next week.
Waiting for his confirmation
Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom
Ran AD Health scan multiple times and the Hardened Paths continues to pop up. The customer has a GPO currently implemented at the top of the domain configuring hardened paths. Why does PC say there are no GPOs created?


Resolution
Remove the quotes from the values for their hardened UNC paths.
